<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-10 my-5">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-dark" style="font-family: sans-serif;">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-muted">Last Updated: May 28, 2026</p>
            <hr class="w-25 mx-auto mt-3" style="border-top: 3px solid #ff385c; opacity: 1;">
        </div>

        <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm p-4 p-md-5" style="border-radius: 20px; background-color: #ffffff;">
            
            <p class="lead text-secondary mb-4">
                Welcome to <strong>Hostio Private Limited</strong>. Your privacy is critically important to us. This Privacy Policy document outlines the types of personal data we collect, how it is processed, and how we protect your security when using our marketplace application.
            </p>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <h3 class="h4 fw-semibold text-dark mb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield me-2" style="color: #ff385c;"></i>1. Information We Collect</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary">When you interact with Hostio, we collect data necessary to provide a smooth room/property rental experience:</p>
                <ul class="text-secondary ps-4">
                    <li class="mb-2"><strong>Account Registration Data:</strong> Your name, email address, password, and contact numbers when you create an account (Sign Up).</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><strong>Listing Details:</strong> If you host a property, we store the title, description, category type, location information, and image parameters you upload to MongoDB.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><strong>Search Analytics:</strong> We temporarily processes typed parameters from our destination search tool to dynamically serve query matches.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <hr class="my-4 opacity-25">

            <div class="mb-4">
                <h3 class="h4 fw-semibold text-dark mb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-gears me-2" style="color: #ff385c;"></i>2. How We Use Your Data</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary">We process your information to maintain and optimize user operations on the app:</p>
                <ul class="text-secondary ps-4">
                    <li class="mb-2">To process application user registration accounts cleanly.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">To display property listings correctly with true location coordinates to prospect travelers.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">To secure your dashboard listings so that only authenticated owners can execute edits or deletes.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <hr class="my-4 opacity-25">

            <div class="mb-4">
                <h3 class="h4 fw-semibold text-dark mb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-lock me-2" style="color: #ff385c;"></i>3. Data Protection & Security</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary">
                    We leverage industry-standard cryptographic practices to safeguard user files. Passwords are fully hashed via secure algorithms prior to cloud saving so that no plain-text credentials are ever exposed in our databases. We do not sell or trade your data to third-party tracking corporations.
                </p>
            </div>

            <hr class="my-4 opacity-25">

            <div class="mb-4">
                <h3 class="h4 fw-semibold text-dark mb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-cookie-bite me-2" style="color: #ff385c;"></i>4. Cookie Preferences</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary">
                    Hostio uses minimal essential functional cookies to keep users authenticated inside active sessions across page reloads. Deactivating cookie options on your local web browser tool may require repetitive login entries during navigational actions.
                </p>
            </div>

            <hr class="my-4 opacity-25">

            <div class="mb-4">
                <h3 class="h4 fw-semibold text-dark mb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope me-2" style="color: #ff385c;"></i>5. Contact Support</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary">
                    If you have security questions regarding your registered account profile records, data deletion updates, or listing configurations, reach out to our administration deck:
                </p>
                <div class="p-3 bg-light rounded-3 mt-2 text-dark border-start border-3" style="border-color: #ff385c !important;">
                    <strong>Hostio Support Operations</strong><br>
                    Email: <span class="text-muted">privacy@hostio.com</span><br>
                    Corporate Node: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center mt-4">
            <a href="/listings" class="text-decoration-none fw-semibold" style="color: #ff385c;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left me-1"></i> Back to Explorations
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>